subject: Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Elizabeth Williams scored 19 points, and No. 7 Duke held on to beat No. 5 Miami, 74-64, in Durham, N.C., clinching the top seed in next week’s Atlantic Coast Conference tournament.
